title: Saikyou Kamizmode! (Saikyo Kamizmode!)
synopsis: Dai Mugen once held an unmatched passion for playing the drums. However, after being defeated by rival drummer Rin Tanba in a competition, he is left questioning where his heart lies and quits as a result.
voices: ['Shin, Yuuki', 'Urushiyama, Yuuki', 'Tada, Keita', 'Yokojima, Wataru', 'Horikoshi, Sena', 'Yamaoka, Yuri', 'Ohtsu, Airi', 'Mineda, Mayu']
